[
  {
    "key": "9bfb0bd4cd4bc586324e7d4465dd2447af9fd31d01ae3861f8544cd7d92435b7",
    "original": "\"We are from the beasts, but the beasts wish to have us back. Distance oneself from nature's primitiveness, prove your worth over Her such that your humanity be held in the grip of your own hands and seen through thine own eyes.\" - Young Anselm",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.TooltipText = \"\\\"We are from the beasts, but the beasts wish to have us back. Distance oneself from nature's primitiveness, prove your worth over Her such that your humanity be held in the grip of your own hands and seen through thine own eyes.\\\" - Young Anselm\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6a72c73709d403097e50b54383b32666a517ba78e5b92502b2b1673bb068eda9",
    "original": "Beasts have always threatened civilization.\nLet us take an Oath of Dominion and stake our claim against the tides of nature!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.ButtonText = \"Beasts have always threatened civilization.\\nLet us take an Oath of Dominion and stake our claim against the tides of nature!\""
  },
  {
    "key": "156f9fecdd0e04a38a78744dacbecc8dbcf80b568930530edb56cf918cfbe141",
    "original": "Oath of Dominion",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.OathName = \"Oath of Dominion\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9c17d0627d4797189d83d35c816d7d6af39237992374c743054432419816fe91",
    "original": "You gain extra Renown for slaying beasts (",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You gain extra Renown for slaying beasts (\" + this.getBonusObjectiveProgress() + \"/\" + this.getBonusObjectiveGoal() + \").\""
  },
  {
    "key": "a4c8559e338539a8a08ea428325fca77ee4af9a257fbda82b330e7d5cd101fb9",
    "original": "Your men have [color=",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Your men have [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.NegativeValue + \"]-10[/color] Resolve and [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.NegativeValue + \"]-5[/color] Melee and Ranged Skill when fighting any other foe.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "a4c8559e338539a8a08ea428325fca77ee4af9a257fbda82b330e7d5cd101fb9",
    "original": "Your men have [color=",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Your men have [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveValue + \"]+20[/color] Resolve and [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveValue + \"]+10[/color] Melee and Ranged Skill when fighting beasts.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "5e98643a00fcff4b08851357fd5db2f8a29cfabb9204b793ac860012af60ab03",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_180.png[/img]There is no more common a menace in this world than that of the common beast. And yet, despite this rampant disease of creatures, very few men are willing to take up arms and go seeking their vanquishment. It is only you all, the %companyname%, who swore an oath to slay the monsters, and slay them you did. With steady hands and stilled hearts, you kept to that Oath.\n\nTriumphant over beasts and monsters, the men are ready to take on whatever's next!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.SuccessText = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_180.png[/img]There is no more common a menace in this world than that of the common beast. And yet, despite this rampant disease of creatures, very few men are willing to take up arms and go seeking their vanquishment. It is only you all, the %companyname%, who swore an oath to slay the monsters, and slay them you did. With steady hands and stilled hearts, you kept to that Oath.\\n\\nTriumphant over beasts and monsters, the men are ready to take on whatever's next!\""
  },
  {
